-- India's Mahindra May Buy Boeing Plant in Australia, Business Standard Says
-- Rakteem Katakey
-- 2010-07-01T01:49:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-01/india-s-mahindra-may-buy-boeing-plant-in-australia-business-standard-says.html

          
          
             Mahindra & Mahindra Ltd. is in talks
with Boeing Co. to buy a plant in Australia, Business Standard
reported, without saying where it got he information. Mumbai-
based Mahindra may buy either a components or aircraft-
manufacturing plant, according to the report.  
